caption: Went on Saturday the place was packed, employees all over the place, disorganized, waited for 25 minutes no one knew who was the next waiting for a table. We ordered coffee and a croissant to go and left. The croissant was delicious. Came back on Sunday because we heard the place serves amazing breakfast. Again, it was a mess Understaffed, no waiting list. We were ,supposedly, the next ones waiting for a table outside. We finally got it after almost 30 minutes and a server came to tell us that we were not supposed to have the table since someone else was waiting before us. None of the people waiting outside got there before us. We told the server and asked him to ask the server that told us that we were the next ones. He said they were understaffed and inquired “ are you really making me do this ? “ .... we stand up and left. No way we are going to spend money in a place that we were not well received. Horrible experience they made us feel like clients are not important at all. Owner/Manager if you know you’ll have a busy business, learn to run your show and be prepared. Get it together. The food could be delicious but the service was horrible. Not planning to give them another opportunity never.
